player createDiaryRecord ["AI",["Dismiss Squad-mate","Select the unit and use the proper option to send them to HQ and you will recover some part of the money you spent on them"]];
player createDiaryRecord ["AI",["Vehicle Squad","Commander Only. Use this option to assign the vehicle you are looking at to any HC squad. Check vehicle status, order them to mount or disembark and automate mounted static squads"]];
player createDiaryRecord ["AI",["Auto Rearm","Your AI squad-mates will automatically look after and scavenge any ammunition from near corpses, vehicles and ammoboxes if needed. Use this instead of vanilla Rearm radio option"]];
player createDiaryRecord ["AI",["Auto Heal","AI Medic squad-mates will heal other AIâ€™s automatically without the need of giving any orders. If in combat, your AI will use smoke grenades to cover. If there is no medic in the group, AI will use their own medikits."]];
player createDiaryRecord ["AI",["AI Radio","Aims to simulate lack of radio communications with AI. As long as personal radios are locked to the Arsenal, your AI squad-mates will have no radio. Without radio, if AI gets too far away, as soon as they accomplish their leader's last order they will get lost and return to the leader position in search of contact with him. To avoid this, you may scavenge some radios from AAF (AutoRearm feature will do) or let the AI use a military vehicle which has long range radios. If enough time passes without meeting each other, they will return back to the HQ."]];
player createDiaryRecord ["AI",["AI Control","Select a squad-mate or HC Group to gain direct control over them for a limited time"]];
player createDiaryRecord ["AI",["Recruit","You may recruit up to 9 AI squad-mates in some FIA flags plus the HQ flag."]];

